  <Summary>Pentagram of Horror is a new horror anthology with each issue being a standalone story. Every action has consequences, no matter whether you are on the side of wrong or right. Everyone, sooner or later, pays the price for their choices.

This is what the sheriff of a small and dusty town in the middle of the desert will discover. He is intent on hunting down a dangerous outlaw who, according to rumors, is in possession of special shamanistic abilities. He should have left well enough alone...</Summary>
